---
title: Rotating Certificates
---

This section specifies the procedure to follow to check expiration dates
and rotate certificates.

To rotate the Services TLS CA and its leaf certificates,
use one of the following procedures:

- If running Ops Manager 2.9, follow the procedure in
[Rotate the Services TLS CA and Its Leaf Certificates](https://docs.pivotal.io/ops-manager/2-9/security/pcf-infrastructure/advanced-certificate-rotation.html#services-rotation).
- If running Ops Manager 2.8, follow the procedure in
[Rotating the Services TLS CA and Its Leaf Certificates](https://docs.pivotal.io/ops-manager/2-8/security/pcf-infrastructure/services_tls_ca_rotate.html).
